INSERT INTO `wp_trs_posts` VALUES (20, 1, '2009-07-18 11:01:35', '2009-07-18 18:01:35', '<strong>You may have read elsewhere that titanium rings cannot be resized. <a title="Learn more about Exotica Jewelry and Chris and Sandy Boothe" href="/about-exotica-jewelry" target="_self">Exotica Jewelry</a> has developed techniques for both enlarging and reducing the size of titanium rings.</strong>\r\n\r\n» <a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing"><strong>Request a price quote for your titanium ring.</strong></a>\r\n<h3>Enlarging a ring</h3>\r\n<strong>We can usually enlarge rings if the change is no more than two sizes bigger.</strong> If the ring is thin to begin with (the thickness of the cross-section, not the width of the ring), we may not be able to enlarge more than one-half to one size bigger. If there are gemstones, there could be an extra charge depending on how deeply the points of the stones are sunk. We cannot resize tension-set rings but we can resize some rings with prong settings.\r\n<h4>Enlarging Costs:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Titanium rings without gemstones: $50</li>\r\n	<li>Titanium rings with gemstones: Please <a href="/order-a-resizing">contact us</a> for a quote</li>\r\n	<li><a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing">Place an order for resizing your titanium ring</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Reducing a ring</h3>\r\n<strong>We can reduce as much as is necessary.</strong> However, if the reduction is more than two sizes, the ring will be noticeably thicker. Some rings with gemstones will have an additional charge per stone.\r\n<h4>Reduction Costs:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>$75 plus $5 per gemstone</li>\r\n	<li><a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing">Place an order for resizing your titanium ring</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBelow are before and after photographs of a ring we reduced one size. We added material to the inside of the ring to make it smaller and we refurbished the finish of the ring.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/resizesmallerbefore-small.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-16" style="border: 1px #000 solid;" title="Titanium ring before resizing" src="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/resizesmallerbefore-small-150x150.jpg" alt="Before" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/resizesmallerafter-small.jpg"><img class="alignleft size-thumbnail wp-image-17" style="border: 1px #000 solid;" title="Titanium ring after resizing" src="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/resizesmallerafter-small-150x150.jpg" alt="After" width="150" height="150" /></a>\r\n<h3 style="clear:left; padding-top:1em;">Engraving is free for all resized rings</h3>\r\nFor rings without gemstones, we can fit up to 40 characters, including spaces. Rings with stones will accommodate fewer characters\r\n\r\nEngraving charges without resizing:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>$25 for one line (40 characters including spaces for rings with no gemstones)</li>\r\n	<li>$35 for two lines (approx. 80 characters) using a tiny font for rings with no stone</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe have two engraving typefaces, script style and modified block style (<em>click to enlarge</em>):\r\n\r\n<a href="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-ss_l.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-6" title="Script Style Engraving" src="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-ss_l-150x65.jpg" alt="Script style engraving" width="150" height="65" /></a> <a href="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-mb_l.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-thumbnail wp-image-15" title="Block Style Engraving" src="http://titaniumresizing.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/05/engrave-mb_l-150x67.jpg" alt="Block style engraving" width="150" height="67" /></a>\r\n<h3>Shipping Charges</h3>\r\nThe shipping cost depends on the value of each ring. Shipping through the post office is the least expensive, about $10 for rings valued at $100. Shipping with tracking is also available through 2-day UPS or FedEx for about $16. <strong>Tell us the value of your ring and how you would like it shipped and we’ll give you the exact shipping charge.</strong><em><strong><a href="http://www.ringsforever.com"></a></strong></em><!--more-->', 'We Can Resize Your Titanium Ring!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision', '', '', '2009-07-18 11:01:35', '2009-07-18 18:01:35', '', 4, 'http://titaniumresizing.com/4-revision', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
