INSERT INTO `wp_trs_posts` VALUES (26, 2, '2010-10-04 22:48:36', '2010-10-05 05:48:36', '<strong>You may have read elsewhere that titanium rings cannot be resized. <a title="Learn more about Exotica Jewelry and Chris and Sandy Boothe" href="/about-exotica-jewelry" target="_self">Exotica Jewelry</a> has developed techniques for both enlarging and reducing the size of titanium rings.</strong>\r\n\r\n» <a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing"><strong>Request a price quote for your titanium ring.</strong></a>\r\n<h3>Enlarging a ring</h3>\r\n<strong>We can usually enlarge rings if the change is no more than two sizes bigger.</strong> If the ring is thin to begin with (the thickness of the cross-section, not the width of the ring), we may not be able to enlarge more than one-half to one size bigger. If there are gemstones, there could be an extra charge depending on how deeply the points of the stones are sunk. We need to see photographs of tension-set and prong-set rings to know whether or not we can resize them..\r\n<h4>Enlarging Costs:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Titanium rings without gemstones: $50</li>\r\n	<li>Titanium rings with gemstones: Please <a href="/order-a-resizing">contact us</a> for a quote</li>\r\n	<li><a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing">Place an order for resizing your titanium ring</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Reducing a ring</h3>\r\n<strong>We can reduce as much as is necessary.</strong> However, if the reduction is more than two sizes, the ring will be noticeably thicker and costs more. Some rings with gemstones will have an additional charge per stone.\r\n<h4>Reduction Costs:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>$75 plus $5 per gemstone for reduction up to 2 sizes smaller; $100 for reducing more than 2 sizes</li>\r\n	<li><a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="/order-a-resizing">Place an order for resizing your titanium ring</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBelow are before and a