e-mb_l-150x67.jpg" alt="Block style engraving" width="150" height="67" /></a>\r\n<h3>Shipping Charges</h3>\r\nThe shipping cost depends on the value of each ring. Shipping through the post office is the least expensive, about $10 for rings valued at $100. Shipping with tracking is also available through 2-day UPS or FedEx for about $16. <strong>Tell us the value of your ring and how you would like it shipped and we’ll give you the exact shipping charge.</strong>\r\n\r\n» <a title="Place your order for a titanium ring resizing" href="../order-a-resizing"><strong>Request a price quote for your titanium ring.</strong></a>', 'We Can Resize Your Titanium Ring!', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '4-revision-4', '', '', '2010-10-04 22:48:36', '2010-10-05 05:48:36', '', 4, 'http://titaniumresizing.com/4-revision-4', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
